      <title>特朗普暗示即将加征关税，加元接近新冠疫情时期低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/loonie-nears-covid-era-low-as-trump-signals-looming-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示将很快对美国邻国征收关税，随后加元跌至近五年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/loonie-nears-covid-era-low-as-trump-signals-looming-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:31:02 GMT</pubDate>
